{"lastModified":1758892876071,"uri":"c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nNAYK 3: The Perfect Holiday Experience\n\nNayk 3 motor yacht is waiting for you for a holiday experience full of luxury, comfort and unforgettable memories! This unique ship was designed to offer you and your loved ones a special escape. With its superior comfort and unique features, Nayk 3 opens the doors to a dreamy holiday.\n\nYacht a has an elegant interior design, every detail of which has been carefully thought out. A spacious and spacious Master cabin located on the main deck offers a privileged accommodation experience. In addition, 3 double cabins and 2 twin cabins maximize the comfort and convenience of your guests. Each cabin has a private bathroom and toilet.\n\nMotor Yacht is equipped with the most advanced maritime technology. Our experienced crew offers you a peaceful and safe journey. You can enjoy your holiday with the yacht’s spacious deck, private sunbathing cushions and comfortable seating areas. Thanks to the ship’s modern navigation and safety equipment, you will have a safe travel experience.\n\nNayk 3 offers a range of entertainment and activity options to make your holiday unforgettable. You can go water skiing in the sea, fishing, exploring the bottom of the sea with snorkeling. At sunset, you can have a pleasant dinner on the deck or relax in the luxurious interiors. Nayk 3 is designed for you to enjoy every moment.\n\nBy taking a blue cruise with Nayk 3, you can explore the most beautiful bays and coasts of Turkey. Bodrum, Fethiye, Gocek and more – you can accumulate unforgettable memories in these wonderful destinations. The routes of Nayk  offer you the unique beauties of nature and the sea.\n\nYacht is waiting for you to offer a holiday experience full of luxury, comfort and pleasant memories. If you want to spend an unforgettable holiday with your family, friends or loved ones, you can choose Nayk 3. We are here to provide you with the best service with our professional crew and state-of-the-art equipment. Book now to experience your dream vacation with Nayk!","blueprint":{"name":"NAYK 3","images":["/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d47104d0-9ada-11f0-8fa4-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d4813170-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d4734ec0-9ada-11f0-8fa5-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d4717a00-9ada-11f0-8fa4-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d4728b70-9ada-11f0-8fa5-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d4837b61-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d4741210-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d47ee780-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d473c3f0-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d47300a0-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d47ff8f0-9ada-11f0-8fa6-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::779394a6-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::d471c820-9ada-11f0-8fa5-0726d976e02c/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644881::vessel::